@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Me";
}

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
            <p>Welcome to my digital journal. This space serves as my personal sanctuary where I capture thoughts, reflections, and moments that matter to me.</p>
            
            <p>I believe in the power of written words to preserve memories, clarify thoughts, and connect with others who might find meaning in shared experiences. This journal is my attempt to maintain that timeless tradition of putting pen to paper—or in this case, fingers to keyboard.</p>
            
            <p>Here you'll find musings on life, book recommendations, personal growth insights, and observations about the world around us. Each entry is written with the same care and intention I would put into a handwritten journal entry.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for taking the time to read and for joining me on this journey of reflection and discovery.</p>
        </div>
        
